Assets.Name: Nike SB - Highs - Unlucky (v2)
Assets.Description:
Compatible game version: 0.0.0.5x or 4.24.3

In order for these shoes to work in game and not crash your shit, Go to your UserEngine.ini file and add  

[/Script/Engine.RendererSettings]
r.LightPropagationVolume = False

This file is located in Session/SessionGame/Config/

Save and install the shoes. Massive thank you to Chuy for finding this fix.
Replaces Mid-Toe Cup shoe.

A HUGE thank you to Redgouf for all his help and amazing 3D model.

Replaces Mid-Top Cup shoe in game.

My Session Catalog: https://pastebin.com/raw/D4e1dfZ6

For my latest releases: https://github.com/WattieSession/SessionMods/releases
